data.description: Discover the essence of country living at 161 Bly Hollow Rd, where a charming 3-bedroom home, fully remodeled for modern comfort, rests on an expansive 60-acre property. The home features one bathroom, making it perfect for cozy family living. This unique property offers more than just a home; it provides you with 60 acres of endless possibilities. A tranquil creek runs behind the home, adding to the natural beauty and charm. Whether you're a nature enthusiast, a hobbyist farmer, or seeking peaceful seclusion, this property can accommodate your dreams. Explore your own private oasis, cultivate a garden, or enjoy outdoor activities on this picturesque land. When it's time to relax, the home offers a comfortable retreat amidst the natural splendor.
